<br>
I was wondering what fellow magi's opinions are on which trade skills they develop and find useful. If I can, I'd like to put most of my points into research so I don't have to search and buy components, but I can put one point into other skills and work them up the normal way.<br>
<br>
Anbody have any suggestions?<br>
<br>
